ield, and their interplay may also be relevant for the thermal processes\noccurring in the plasma of solar flares. The considered example suggests that\nour method will be beneficial for both the modeling of observed eruptive events\nand theoretical studies of eruptions in idealized magnetic configurations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 May 2022 00:16:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 4 Aug 2022 22:43:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 18 Aug 2022 21:57:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-14"}
