lenges the growth of cm-sized pebbles into km-sized\nobjects. Interstellar planetesimals play a pivotal role in our understanding of\nplanetary system formation and evolution and point to the possibility that one\nday, we will be able to hold a fragment from another world in our hand.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 May 2022 13:47:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-10"}
